high_descs: Turn to the right and move toward the refrigerator then turn to the left once past the counter, move toward the white range, then turn left and face the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter between the spoon on the left and the loaf of bread on the right.
Turn left and move to the end of the counter, then turn left and move to the blue toaster between the coffee maker and the refrigerator.
Use the knife to slice half the tomato in front of the toaster into slices.
Turn left and move to the microwave to the right of the range.
Open the microwave door, place the knife on the plate in the microwave, then close the microwave door.
Turn around and move toward the refrigerator then turn left and face the sliced tomato on the counter.
Pick up one tomato slice from the sliced tomato on the counter.
Turn left and move to the microwave above the dishwasher.
Open the microwave door, place the tomato slice to the rear of the knife on the plate, microwave the slice, then remove the tomato slice from the microwave and then close the microwave door.
Turn to the right and face the sink in front of the window.
Place the tomato slice in front of the egg in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked tomato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, go past the counter, turn left, go to the counter to the left of the oven, turn left to face the counter.
Take the knife from the counter on the right.
Turn left, walk to the end of the counter, turn left, go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Turn left, go to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around, go back to the counter with the tomato on the left.
Take a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn left, go to the microwave.
Cook the tomato in the microwave, take the tomato from the microwave.
Turn right to face the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in a sink.

high_descs: Turn right, head towards the middle of the counter and fridge, turn left, head towards the slice of bread on the counter, and then turn left to face the lettuce.
Pick up the knife in front of the lettuce.
Turn around and head towards the coffee maker.
Slice the tomato in front of the coffee maker into several slices.
Turn left and head towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the knife in it, and close the microwave.
Turn around and head towards the coffee maker on your left.
Pick up a middle slice of tomato next to the coffee maker.
Turn left and head towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the tomato in it, heat it cup, and take it back out.
Turn right to face the sink.
Place the slice of tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the warm slice of tomato in the sink.
